text: Like new and move in ready. This 2020 built 3 bed 1.75 bath rambler is located in a nice neighborhood with other newer homes. Inside, an open concept floor plan with engineered plank flooring, upgraded kitchen cabinets, stainless appliances, recessed lighting, & a ductless heating & cooling system for those hot summer days. The spacious bathrooms have beautiful ceramic tile flooring & solid surface countertops. The owners suite has its own full bath, walk-in closet, and a large sliding glass door that leads you to your outdoor patio & spacious backyard. Come and take a look today!

One other bedroom down and two more bedrooms upstairs with full bath. The back yard is fenced and pet ready. Located across the street from Kwann Lake and within walking distance of the pool and clubhouse. Village amenities include a 9 hole golf course with snack bar, marina, salt water parks, beaches, tennis and pickleball courts, club house, pool, 2 man made lakes and 24 hour manned gated security.
This bright and airy waterfront condominium has a pool, private beach, fantastic views of the Salish Sea and is located right next to the Point Roberts Marina. Affordable waterfront living.

Experience epic fun at Grand Bay condos and beach! Vibrant seaside-style resort life w/in golf cart zone w/nearby Birch Bay restaurants, Beach Cat Brewery, library, parks. Full time or second home. PRICE REDUCED! May qualify for WSHFC Down Payment Assistance Prog. Seller will pay $2000 toward buyer closing costs.
